\033[1m\033[32mADD\033[0m - Create a new script in the current mango repo

\033[1mUSAGE:\033[0m
    mango @add [script_name] (-b, --bind [command_name ...]) (-s, --source) (--noopen)

\033[1mDESCRIPTION:\033[0m
    Creates a new script in the current mango repository and opens it in the default editor.
    If the script already exists, it will be opened for editing.
    Automatically binds the script to commands if specified.

\033[1mARGUMENTS:\033[0m
    script_name    Name of the script to create

\033[1mOPTIONS:\033[0m
    -b, --bind      Bind the script to specified command names
    -s, --source    Enable source mode for the script
    --noopen        Create script without opening in editor

\033[1mEXAMPLES:\033[0m
    mango @add myscript
    mango @add myscript -b cmd1 cmd2
    mango @add myscript --noopen
    mango @add myscript -s